    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h2 id="Artificialn-Intelligence"><a href="#Artificialn-Intelligence" class="headerlink" title="Artificialn Intelligence"></a>Artificialn Intelligence</h2><h3 id="概念"><a href="#概念" class="headerlink" title="概念"></a>概念</h3><p>AI: Intelligence displayed by mechines. </p><h3 id="扮演的角色"><a href="#扮演的角色" class="headerlink" title="扮演的角色"></a>扮演的角色</h3><ol><li><p>大数据与AI的关系<br>big data -&gt;feed to -&gt; AI<br>then data become useful knowledge</p></li><li><p>不同概念的定位<br>Big data: Fuel (Just Data)<br>AI: Car (program, algrithm, method)<br>ML: a part of AI (more like tools that self-improve)</p></li><li><p>AI=Knowledge Representation+Search</p></li></ol><h3 id="常用领域"><a href="#常用领域" class="headerlink" title="常用领域"></a>常用领域</h3><p>Some AI topics:<br>    1. Machine Vision<br>    2. Planning<br>    3. Natural language understanding<br>    4. Robotics<br>    5. Constraint satisfaction<br>    6. Mechine Learning</p><h2 id="Computation-in-Finance"><a href="#Computation-in-Finance" class="headerlink" title="Computation in Finance"></a>Computation in Finance</h2><h3 id="Financial-market"><a href="#Financial-market" class="headerlink" title="Financial market"></a>Financial market</h3><ol><li>Speed is everthing</li><li>Seeking rather than running: find hidden oppotunities</li></ol><h3 id="Computation-Finance"><a href="#Computation-Finance" class="headerlink" title="Computation Finance"></a>Computation Finance</h3><p>Computation Finance: Applying advanced computing methods to finance with the aim to exploit synergy</p><ol><li>trader trying to find opptunities</li><li>computer expert lend a hand to trader</li><li>computer can seek for the pattern quickly</li><li>trader can give the direction to seek</li><li>make a team with computer expert</li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
