    <title>Pytorch框架部署与一些基础使用</title>
    <link href="https://blog.cyersc.com/posts/c32a948c.html"/>
    <id>https://blog.cyersc.com/posts/c32a948c.html</id>
    <published>2022-02-14T02:57:58.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-02-18T05:27:09.606Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h1 id="PyTorch框架是什么？"><a href="#PyTorch框架是什么？" class="headerlink" title="PyTorch框架是什么？"></a>PyTorch框架是什么？</h1><p>在<a href="https://pytorch.apachecn.org/#/docs/1.7/README">PyTorch 中文官方教程 1.7</a>中对于PyTorch的描述如下：</p><blockquote><p>PyTorch 是基于以下两个目的而打造的python科学计算框架：</p><ol><li>无缝替换NumPy，并且通过利用GPU的算力来实现神经网络的加速。</li><li>通过自动微分机制，来让神经网络的实现变得更加容易。</li></ol></blockquote><h1 id="PyTorch框架的部署"><a href="#PyTorch框架的部署" class="headerlink" title="PyTorch框架的部署"></a>PyTorch框架的部署</h1><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><ol><li>Anaconda</li></ol><p>通过官网选择安装包下载安装即可：<a href="https://www.anaconda.com/">Anaconda | The World’s Most Popular Data Science Platform</a><br>启动Anaconda Prompt后看到base环境即为安装成功。</p><ol start="2"><li>管理环境<br>新建和激活pytorch专用环境：</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs bash">conda create -n pytorch python=3.6 <span class="hljs-comment">#创建新环境</span><br>conda activate pytorch <span class="hljs-comment">#激活环境，后会看到(base)变成(pytorch)</span><br>pip list <span class="hljs-comment">#检查环境中包的情况</span><br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>PyTorch &amp; cuda<br>首先应确定设备显卡是否支持cuda，然后在PyTorch官网<a href="https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/">Start Locally | PyTorch</a>选择合适的配置后，复制安装指令到Anaconda Prompt。</li></ol><p>在环境中验证安装是否成功：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> torch<br>torch.cuda.is_available()<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>返回true。</p><h2 id="编辑器"><a href="#编辑器" class="headerlink" title="编辑器"></a>编辑器</h2><ol><li><p>Pycharm<br>通过官网下载安装：<a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/pycharm/">PyCharm: the Python IDE for Professional Developers by JetBrains</a></p></li><li><p>Jupyter<br>安装与打开：</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs bash">conda install nb_conda<br>jupyter notebook<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用shift+enter 运行下述代码块对环境配置进行验证：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> torch<br>torch.cuda.is_available()<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>返回true。</p>]]></content>
    
    
